name: cat food (itch) (q1)
description:
it's a cat game...

made for sylvie's jam #1

.

this game has sound! but it may take a while to load.

controls
ARROW KEYS to move/stand/sit
SPACEBAR to throw fish
you must be SITTING to operate the boat!
you must be STANDING to leave the boat!

using polyducks's japanese woodblock palette

shop doodles by my friend @Houn :)
